 ** [Name](#API_GetAnycastIpList_ResponseSyntax) **   <a name="cloudfront-GetAnycastIpList-response-Name"></a>
The name of the Anycast static IP list.  
Type: String  
Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 64.  
